Just let me out!

did I do to deserve this?

target: Rise from the darkness!

target: Then so shall I.

If the water were
any deeper, I'd drown!
target:
If the water were
any deeper, I'd drown!

My brain...
I think I boiled it.
target:
My brain...
I think I boiled it.

scalp you right here.

hair, Midlander, and I'll

without, the wine within.

discovered, ladies.

target:
I can get twice as much
in Ul'dah for half the price!

for ten score malms!
target:
Last stop for supplies
for ten score malms!

ye say? Cor!

certainly grown
lively of late.

These must all be moved
to the Find at once.

These must all be moved
to the Find at once.

you have to get by me first!
target:
You want this aetheryte,
you have to get by me first!

Naught but
weeds, all of it.
target:
Naught but
weeds, all of it.

source:
I'm boiling
in this armor.
target:
I'm boiling
in this armor.

source:
The soft flesh under the
jaw. That's their weak spot.
target:
The soft flesh under the
jaw. That's their weak spot.

a whole dragon.
target:
Feels like I ate
a whole dragon.

over to my bunk, squire?

I'd be warmer in
bed with a corpse.

I'd be warmer in
bed with a corpse.

The visor keeps my
eyes from freezing shut.

The visor keeps my
eyes from freezing shut.

Well, you're obviously not

Well, you're obviously not
a giant. You may pass.

from the north face.

from the north face.

dig from the south.

dig from the south.

in a place as this.

in a place as this.

wrought from a single stone!

wrought from a single stone!

wouldn't wander too far.

wouldn't wander too far.

wheat and a box of

You call these documents research?
They're not even worth wiping the privy floor with!

You call these documents research?
They're not even worth wiping the privy floor with!

What wretched weather to be laboring in.
As if this work weren't hard enough!
target:
What wretched weather to be laboring in.
As if this work weren't hard enough!

If any of these get too damp,
it could spell trouble for us.

If any of these get too damp,
it could spell trouble for us.

Why did I live,
when so many others...?

Why did I live,
when so many others...?

The air is ice itself.
I may freeze to death at this rate.

The air is ice itself.
I may freeze to death at this rate.

target: What happened to those supplies you ordered a while back?

target: Its temperament appears to be somewhat more stable, to be sure.

source: I vote philosopher's carrots. They'll keep us light on our feet!
target: I vote philosopher's carrots. They'll keep us light on our feet!

target: No, no─iron carrots first. We won't get far without bulging thews!

target: What food do you think mankind likes?

target: Well, carrots, surely.

target: All right, this water quality won't check itself! Let's get to it.

target: Visual inspection complete. Status: crystal clear!

target: <sniff> <sniff> Scent inspection complete. Status: bracing!

target: How goes the system change?

source: Oh, about as well as can be expected.

target: <sniffle> Wh-Where's Daddy? D-Did he...?

target: My arm. Argh, it's killing me...!

target: I'm afraid you have a bit too much cargo for me to collect...

What a curious custom,
this Heavensturn business.

Какая любопытная традиция,

target: <var 1A 02 /var>Всё ещё<var 1A 01 /var> он имеет наглость отвергать меня? Ба! Я готова выпотрошить его, как только он покажется!

target: В письме говорилось, что дуэль должна состояться здесь.

target: А что, «Золотое блюдце» такое же замечательное, как я себе представлял, и даже больше!

source: I wonder what varieties of pudding they serve in this place?

source: Well an' good to follow your heart─just don't follow it off a cliff.
target: Well an' good to follow your heart─just don't follow it off a cliff.

source: “Don't follow heart off cliff”... Got it, sir!
target: “Don't follow heart off cliff”... Got it, sir!

source: Oh, the places I want to see!
target: Oh, the places I want to see!

target: Мне очень нравится этот слон в комнате!

source: Look, look! It's the Azure Elephant!
target: Смотрите, смотрите! Это Лазурный Слон!

source: I daresay today's gains shall be plentiful.
target: Смею предположить, что сегодняшняя прибыль будет обильной.

target: За Золотое Блюдце! <var 1A 02 /var> На этот раз<var 1A 01 /var> Кактусовый горшочек наш!

source: Coming here together feels like a dream.

source: No residue detected. Table ready.

source: How many have you had!?
target: Сколько их у тебя было?!

source: Standing by for patron arrival.

source: Oh, they'll want to hear this...
target: Oh, they'll want to hear this...

source: Right...there!
